  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6755.88 sitting right in the thick negative gamma zone (-8710.4M at 6755), dealers are forced to buy this rally as they're short gamma in breakout regime. The massive negative GEX wall at 6750 (-11.5B) that we just broke through is now acting as support, while dealers will become sellers into any push toward the 6775 positive gamma wall (+6.7B). Expect continued volatile, trending moves with dealers amplifying momentum - any dip back toward 6750 triggers dealer buying, while rallies toward 6775 face increasing dealer selling pressure.\n\n**Bottom line:** Price should trend higher with volatile swings until hitting resistance around 6775.",
